OL,3,CTeachers to be consulted on strike
OL,4,Caction for 'better pay and funding'
OL,6,FThe country's largest teaching union
OL,7,Fhas agreed to launch an indicative
OL,8,Fballot over potential strike action
OL,9,Ffor "better pay and funding".
OL,11,FThe National Education Union (NEU)
OL,12,Fsaid the ballot in February would ask
OL,13,Fmembers' willingness "to take strike
OL,14,Faction on the issue of continued
OL,15,Fausterity in education".
