OL,6,FThe union added that its executive had
OL,7,Fapproved launching a campaign to
OL,8,F"build a case over the coming months
OL,9,Ffor better pay and funding" and would
OL,10,Fbe "taking the argument to government,
OL,11,Fto parents and the profession".
OL,13,FIt said its national executive met on
OL,14,FSaturday to "discuss the crisis in
OL,15,Feducation funding and teacher pay".
OL,17,FSpeaking after the meeting, Daniel
OL,18,FKebede, general secretary of the NEU,
OL,19,Fsaid: "This week's budget failed to
OL,20,Faddress the existential crisis our
OL,21,Fschools are facing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
