OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"The Government's proposed 6.5% pay
OL,12,Frise for teachers over three years,
OL,13,Fwith no extra money behind it, will
OL,14,Fonly worsen the situation.
OL,16,F"Cold classrooms, leaking roofs,
OL,17,Fbroken toilets. Staff leaving and
OL,18,Fnever replaced. Workload soaring as a
OL,19,Fresult. We cannot endure any more cuts
OL,20,Fto education.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
