OL,4,Caction for 'better pay and funding'
OL,6,F"The School Teachers' Review Body is
OL,7,Fexpected to send its report on teacher
OL,8,Fpay to the secretary of state in
OL,9,FFebruary 2026.
OL,11,F"If the Government responds and sticks
OL,12,Fwith an under-inflation and unfunded
OL,13,F6.5%, then we will know that yet more
OL,14,Fcuts are on the horizon.
OL,16,F"That is why the NEU executive has
OL,17,Fapproved the launch of a campaign to
OL,18,Fsave education and build a case over
OL,19,Fthe coming months for better pay and
OL,20,Ffunding.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
