OL,6,F"It is in the Government's gift to
OL,7,Favoid a confrontation with the
OL,8,Fprofession. Education is running on
OL,9,Fempty. We will not stand by as this
OL,10,FGovernment continues to underfund our
OL,11,Fschools and drive education into the
OL,12,Fground.
OL,14,F"As a union we are prepared to take
OL,15,Fwhatever action is necessary to save
OL,16,Four schools."
